<TEXT>
Credit du Nord, the retail banking arm of the Paribas financial group,
yesterday announced a sharp increase in net losses to FFr610.9m (Dollars
106m) for last year from FFr253.4m in 1992
Mr Bernard Auberger, chairman, said the bank was aiming to break even this
