USM-quoted Learmonth and Burchett Management Systems plunged 44 to 96p after
announcing that difficult trading conditions meant group results for the
year to April were likely to fall 'well short' of market forecasts.
Advertising group Gold Greenlees Trott dropped 55 to 184p on its second
