FT  18 MAR 94 / International Company News: Trump wins licence for casino
project
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By RICHARD TOMKINS
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Donald Trump, the New York developer and casino operator who came close
to bankruptcy three years ago, yesterday said he had won a licence from the
Mississippi Gaming Commission to go ahead with a proposed casino project in
Gulfport, Mississippi.
The casino, due to open early next year, will take the form of a riverboat
docked next to the Marine Life Oceanarium, which Mr Trump plans to renovate.
