</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An increased provision of Pounds 1.65m against land holdings left Edmond
Holdings, the Northampton-based housebuilder, with higher pre-tax losses of
Pounds 1.89m for the 1993 year on turnover lower at Pounds 11m.
