the first time in five years, resulting in a profit for the period of Pounds
61,000 before provisions and tax.
The company said that in view of the better trading and its underlying
strength it was proposing to maintain the final dividend at 0.15p for a
total of 0.3p (0.5p). Losses per share were 3.1p (1.5p).
